     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts FRNonHumanSubjectLMCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"FRNonHumanSubjectLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcFRNonHumanSubjectLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-sujet-non-humain</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-sujet-non-humain</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSujetNonHumain</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDASujetNonHumain</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSujetNonHumain.sujet</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDASujetNonHumain.subject.relatedSubject.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMSujetNonHumain.adresse</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDASujetNonHumain.subject.relatedSubject.addr</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 2 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-sujet-non-humain</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-observation-laboratory-report-results-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td><td><b>Commentaire</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRCDASujetNonHumain</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRObservationLaboratoryReportResultsDocument.specimen</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRCDASujetNonHumain.subject.relatedSubject.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRObservationLaboratoryReportResultsDocument.specimen.subject:Substance</td><td>specimen.subject = Reference(Substance).</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 3 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-sujet-non-humain</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/substance</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRCDASujetNonHumain.subject.relatedSubject.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Substance.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDASujetNonHumain.subject.relatedSubject.code.qualifier.value</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Substance.category</td></tr></table></div>"
